  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this research study is to show that features derived from data gathered using
      SHIMMER wearable sensor platform can capture adherence and proficiency in the performance of
      exercises that are part of Tai Chi interventions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
